## Git Workflow

- Always branch from `main`
- Feature branches: `feature/<name>`
- Bug fix branches: `fix/<name>`
- Never commit directly to `main`

## Session Workflow

- Start: `/gamet-checkpoint` or just describe what you want to build
- Build: `/gamet-orchestrator "feature description"` for full pipeline
- Discover: `/gamet-discovery` for what to build next
- Review: `/gamet-panel` for GAMET review
- End: `/gamet-checkpoint` to save state

